Santos CANCEL
v.
COMMISSIONER OF CORRECTION Supreme Court of Connecticut. Decided June 19, 2019

The petitioner Santos Cancel's petition for certification to appeal from the Appellate Court, 189 Conn.App. 667, 208 A.3d 1256 (2019), is denied.

MULLINS, J., did not participate in the consideration of or decision on this petition.
